<plot>A documentary crew interviews Craig Johnson III regarding his recent membership in an international group known as Desk Dwellers United (DDU). Through a series of interviews, Living Under Linda's Desk offers a rare glimpse into the world of a workaholic who has a new look and appreciation of life by living under a desk of an office worker. Craig, Linda and Craig's family share how the DDU movement had influenced their lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?339234</url></doc>
